Now we can calculate the average dependency distance by summing the distances and dividing by the number of dependencies:

Distances: 1 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 0 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 2 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 2 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 0 + 1 + 2 + 1 + 0 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 2 + 16 + 35 = 67

